## Draft / exploratory specification artifacts
## -------------------------------------------------

reference-execution-sketch.md

## -------------------------------------------------
## Public normative specifications (explicitly tracked)
## -------------------------------------------------

!docs/trace-schema.md
!docs/provenance-payload.md

